only the first (generally bad) one aired on christmas
the doctor the widow and the wardrobe
moffat wrote some awful christmas specials but opened and closed with probably the best ones
summary: Which Season the Christmas Specials Belong in:
title: Which Season the Christmas Specials Belong in:
body:
• The Christmas Invasion: Season 2
  • The Runaway Bride: Season 2
  • Voyage of the Damned: Season 3
  • The Next Doctor and The End of Time, Part One: The David Tennant Specials, obviously
  • A Christmas Carol: Season 5
  • The Doctor, The Widow, and The Wardrobe: Season 7A
  • The Snowmen: Season 7B
  • The Time of the Doctor: Season 7C
  • Last Christmas: Season 9
  • The Husbands of River Song: Season 9
  • The Return of Doctor Mysterio: Season 9
  • Twice Upon a Time: Season 10

It’s better to have an unnecessary coda than to ruin a beginning. Only place it forward when it’s setting up the next season.
